        <div class="mainText">
            <div class="mainText__title">Long headline for two lines for attention and evolving</div>
            <div class="mainText__desc">With the new AirPlay 2, you can control your home audio system and the speakers throughout your house.4 You can play a song in the living room and your kitchen at the same time.</div>
